19:# DECISION
23:# PRESIDENT OF VIETNAM NATIONAL UNIVERSITY, HANOI
45:# DECIDES:
47:## Article 1. To issue, together with this Decision, the "Regulations on Management and Attraction of Foreigners Studying at Vietnam National University, Hanoi".
49:## Article 2. This Decision shall take effect from April 1, 2024 and shall replace the "Regulations on Attraction and Management of International Students at Vietnam National University, Hanoi" issued under Decision No. 4848/QĐ-ĐHQGHN dated December 18, 2017 of the President of Vietnam National University, Hanoi, and shall replace the provisions related to exchange students in the "Guidelines for the Implementation of Student Exchange Programs with Foreign Universities at Vietnam National University, Hanoi" issued under Decision No. 3763/QĐ-ĐHQGHN dated November 7, 2012.
51:## Article 3. The Chief of Office, Heads of functional departments, Heads of training units at Vietnam National University, Hanoi, and related organizations and individuals shall be responsible for the implementation of this Decision./.
